    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286280/extras/3412e0f4cd93fc656e7ab309ca0cf209.poster.avif?t=1738875722\" width=512 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286280/extras/3412e0f4cd93fc656e7ab309ca0cf209.webm?t=1738875722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286280/extras/3412e0f4cd93fc656e7ab309ca0cf209.mp4?t=1738875722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Spacepunk Survival</strong> is a multiplayer first-person shooter where you and your teammates must survive for as long as you can in the dark and hostile environment of the Iapetus Station, a once thriving laboratory which is now overrun by monstrous alien creatures. Boasting amazing retro graphics, Spacepunk pays homage to the great sci-fi and retrofuturistic works of the past.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Face dangerous aliens</h2>From swarming hordes to hulking beasts, a variety of aliens lurk in Iapetus, all of them ready to kill you on first sight. Will you fend off their endless assaults, or will the alien ranks overrun you?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the station</h2>Full of dark corridors and narrow passages, the station holds many secrets. Be ready to change your play on the fly when you least expect.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play alone or with your friends</h2>Survive the alien incursion alone or with other fellow astronauts. The challenges faced will adapt to the number of survivors, how long will you last?",
